/api/customers	GET	Get all the customers.
/api/customers	POST	Create a customer.
/api/customers/:customers_id	GET	Get a single customer.
/api/customers/:customers_id	PUT	Update a customer with new info.
/api/customers/:customers_id	DELETE	Delete a customer.


/api/persons	GET	Get all the persons.
/api/persons	POST	Create a person.
/api/persons/:persons_id	GET	Get a single person.
/api/persons/:persons_id	PUT	Update a person with new info.
/api/persons/:persons_id	DELETE	Delete a person.
